EVANTIC - Event Ticket Management System
Developed by: Zachary Jordan
Company: Saym Services Inc. (saymservices.com)
Project Website: evantic.quest
Year: 2025

This system includes the following key features:
- Event creation and management with QR code ticketing
- NFT minting for validated tickets
- Cryptocurrency payments via Coinbase Commerce
- Stripe payment integration  
- P2P ticket validation
- Event reputation system
- Ticket resale mechanism
- 69-day data retention with archiving
- Location-based event filtering
- RSS feed functionality
- Windows 98-inspired UI elements

For the complete AGPLv3 license terms, please visit:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.en.html